Drupal installation steps
1.Check System Requirements
.Install XAMPP/WAMP (PHP, MySQL, Apache)
.PHP 8.1+ recommended
2.Download Drupal
.Go to official website
.Download latest version (example: Drupal 10)
3.Extract the File
.Extract the downloaded ZIP file
.Copy the Drupal folder into htdocs (XAMPP)
4.Create Database
.Open http://localhost/phpmyadmin
.Click New
.Create a database (example: drupal_db)
5.Run Installation
.Open browser
.Type: http://localhost/drupal-folder-name
6.Select Language
.Choose your preferred language
7.Choose Installation Profile
.Select Standard
.Click Continue
8.Database Configuration
.Enter database name
.Username: root
.Password: (leave blank if using XAMPP)
9.Site Configuration
.Enâ€¦
